The paper deals with image classification using Deep Learning, specifically Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs), which is a popular topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of Deep Learning also falls under the sub-category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the performance of different models and the use of multi-channel representation, which are topics related to machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of a dataset and the analysis of results, which are topics related to information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper deals with the application of the algorithm to oral health, which falls under the sub-category of multimedia (cs.MM).
